From cf2cd9cf1a8e9ff8cd0c389ccbd727df59545551 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ramanathan Choodamani <rchoodam@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 17 Jul 2025 00:38:44 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:hostapd:MSCS:Add protocol support for Mirrored SCS

Add MLME protocol support for Mirrored SCS protocol.

1. If supported, advertise MSCS in extended capabilities.
2. Add support to receive, parse and process MSCS request action frame.
3. Add support to send MSCS response action frame.

Patch-dependency: r89-01-UPSTREAM-PROTOCOL-CP-HOSTAPD-Register-to-receive-SCS-frame.patch
Patch-work: NA
Tag: MSCS

Signed-off-by: Ramanathan Choodamani <rchoodam@qti.qualcomm.com>
